trong> of protection at its thickest point helps stop thorns and debris.<\/p>","show_segments":true,"segments":5,"active_segment":"4","fill_segments":true,"show_labels":true,"label_left":"","label_middle":"","label_right":"","show_icon":false,"icon":"star"}},"feature_DWbMFp":{"type":"feature","disabled":true,"settings":{"bg_color":"#ffffff","bg_gradient":"","text_color":"#1f1f1f","heading":"Run-flat support","text":"<p>Ride short distances even with a flat tube—slow and steady to get home safely.<\/p>","show_segments":true,"segments":5,"active_segment":"4","fill_segments":true,"show_labels":true,"label_left":"","label_middle":"","label_right":"","show_icon":false,"icon":"star"}},"feature_wCxpte":{"type":"feature","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/tannus_protection.png","bg_color":"#ffffff","bg_gradient":"","text_color":"#1f1f1f","heading":"360° tube coverage","text":"<p>Armour wraps nearly 360° around the tube with up to <strong>15 mm<\/strong> protection where you need it most.<\/p>","show_segments":true,"segments":5,"active_segment":"4","fill_segments":true,"show_labels":true,"label_left":"","label_middle":"","label_right":"","show_icon":false,"icon":"star"}},"feature_biFbHJ":{"type":"feature","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/tannus_armour_insert.png","bg_color":"#ffffff","bg_gradient":"","text_color":"#1f1f1f","heading":"Lower PSI, more comfort","text":"<p>With Armour protecting the tube, you can run lower PSI for extra grip and a smoother ride.<\/p>","show_segments":true,"segments":5,"active_segment":"2","fill_segments":true,"show_labels":true,"label_left":"","label_middle":"","label_right":"","show_icon":false,"icon":"star"}},"feature_iYXNgk":{"type":"feature","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/tannus_protection_2.png","bg_color":"#ffffff","bg_gradient":"","text_color":"#1f1f1f","heading":"Rim protection","text":"<p>Cushions hard hits and helps prevent pinch flats—extra peace of mind on broken pavement and gravel.<\/p>","show_segments":true,"segments":5,"active_segment":"3","fill_segments":true,"show_labels":true,"label_left":"","label_middle":"","label_right":"","show_icon":false,"icon":"star"}}},"block_order":["feature_JVzUKF","feature_DWbMFp","feature_wCxpte","feature_biFbHJ","feature_iYXNgk"],"name":"Key features","settings":{"heading":"Key features","image_max_width":700,"media_aspect_ratio":"1","image_position":"left","segment_position":"over-text"}},"collapsible_tabs_DfhyV6":{"type":"collapsible-tabs","blocks":{"question_hAELRe":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"What size Tannus Armour do I need?","answer":"<p>Match the insert to your tire size. Example: if your tire says <strong>26 × 2.1<\/strong>, choose <strong>Tannus Armour 26 × 2.0–2.5<\/strong>.<\/p><p>Need help with tubes? Use the <a href=\"\\&quot;https:\/\/tannusamerica.com\/products\/tannus-armour#armour_specs\\&quot;\"><strong>Tannus size chart<\/strong><\/a> to pick the right tube size.<\/p><p>🔧 <em>Tip:<\/em> Inner tube size is usually smaller than the tire size—that’s normal.<\/p>"}},"question_iLNpRW":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"What’s the recommended tire pressure?","answer":"<p>Tannus Armour lets you run <strong>lower PSI<\/strong> for comfort and control. Start about <strong>5 PSI lower<\/strong> than your usual pressure, then adjust to feel.<\/p><ul><li>Heavier riders: increase PSI for more support<\/li><li>Lighter riders: keep PSI lower for more cushion<\/li><li>Fat-tire ebikes: do not go below <strong>10 PSI<\/strong><\/li><\/ul>"}},"question_cwMxqD":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"Can I still ride if I get a flat?","answer":"<p>Yes. Armour provides <strong>short-distance run-flat support<\/strong> so you can ride a few miles to a safe spot.<\/p><ul><li>Slow down and avoid rough terrain if the tube is flat<\/li><li>Check your rim and tube before your next ride<\/li><\/ul><p><em>Not recommended<\/em> for sizes: <strong>20 × 3.0+<\/strong> or <strong>26 × 4.0+<\/strong>.<\/p>"}},"question_RyAVXR":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"How do I install Tannus Armour?","answer":"<p>See the step-by-step guide with photos: <a href=\"\\&quot;https:\/\/tannusamerica.com\/pages\/tannus-armour-installation\\&quot;\"><strong>Installation guide<\/strong><\/a>.<\/p><p>Prefer a pro? Visit a local <a href=\"\\&quot;\/pages\/dealer-locator\\&quot;\"><strong>Euphree dealer<\/strong><\/a>.<\/p>"}},"question_aALcWX":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"Do Armour inserts work with ebikes?","answer":"<p>Yes. Armour works with Euphree ebikes and other ebikes. Choose the insert that matches your tire size and follow the PSI guidance for your weight and terrain.<\/p><ul><li>Reduces flats and pinch flats<\/li><li>Improves comfort at lower PSI<\/li><li>Adds rim protection<\/li><\/ul>"}}},"block_order":["question_hAELRe","question_iLNpRW","question_cwMxqD","question_RyAVXR","question_aALcWX"],"name":"Collapsible tabs","settings":{"title":"Tannus Armour Tire Insert FAQ"}},"gallery_zD6JGN":{"type":"gallery","blocks":{"media_qrcGfj":{"type":"media","settings":{"enlarge_media":true,"subheading":"","title":"","button_label":"","link":"","text_alignment":"bottom left"}},"media_rtmDrW":{"type":"media","settings":{"enlarge_media":false,"subheading":"","title":"","button_label":"","link":"","text_alignment":"bottom left"}},"media_DyXna7":{"type":"media","settings":{"enlarge_media":false,"subheading":"","title":"","button_label":"","link":"","text_alignment":"bottom left"}},"media_3aHFTg":{"type":"media","settings":{"enlarge_media":true,"subheading":"","title":"","button_label":"","link":"","text_alignment":"bottom left"}}},"block_order":["media_qrcGfj","media_rtmDrW","media_DyXna7","media_3aHFTg"],"disabled":true,"name":"Gallery","settings":{"grid_desktop":2,"grid_mobile":"1","height":"fixed","desktop_image_height":460,"mobile_image_height":400,"title_size":30,"title_size_mobile":22,"enable_margin":true,"enable_row_spacing":true,"full_width":false,"color_scheme":"default","ena